\c 99
\s Jehovha mutsvene ngaarumbidzwe
\p
\v 1 Jehovha anobata ushe; vanhu ngavabvunde; Iye agere pakati pamakerubhi; nyika ngaizununguswe.
\v 2 Jehovha mukuru paZioni; Ari kumusoro-soro kwavanhu vose.
\v 3 Ngavarumbidze zita renyu guru rinotyisa; Ndiye Mutsvene.
\v 4 Simba ramambo rinodawo kururamisa; Imi munosimbisa kururama, Munotonga muchiruramisa pakati paJakobho.
\v 5 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, Munamate pachitsiko chetsoka dzake; Ndiye Mutsvene.
\v 6 Mosesi naAroni pakati pavapristi vake, NaSamueri pakati pavanodana zita rake; Vakadana kuna Jehovha, iye akavapindura. Akataura navo ari mushongwe yegore;
\s Vakachengeta zvipupuriro zvake nomutemo waakavapa.
\p
\v 8 Makavapindura, Jehovha Mwari wedu;
\p Maiva Mwari aivakanganwira, Kunyange makatsiva zvavaiita.
\v 9 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, Namatai pagomo rake dzvene; Nokuti Jehovha Mwari wedu ndiye
\s Mutsvene.
